<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/spy.svg" />
</head>
<style>
  pre {
    background-color: #eee;
    padding: 1em;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <h1><%= title %></h1>
  <section>
    <h2>serving ads</h2>
    <p>This SSP serve Ads creative by Advertiser to publisher via <code>ad-tag</code></p>
    <p>Ads will embed inside &lt;iframe&gt; or &lt;fencedframe&gt; like below</p>
    <ins class="ads">
      <script class="ssp_tag" src="https://ssp.example/ad-tag.js"></script>
    </ins>

    <h2>inside iframe</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a target="_blank" href="https://ssp.example/ad-tag.html">https://ssp.example/ad-tag.html</a>
      <li><a target="_blank" href="https://ssp.example/ads?advertiser=shop&id=1f45e">https://ssp.example/ads?advertiser=shop&id=1f45e</a>
    </ul>
    <h2>embed script</h2>
    <p>3rd party script provided by ssp should embed as below</p>
    <pre>
&lt;ins class="ads"&gt;
  &lt;script class="ssp_tag" src="https://ssp.example/ad-tag.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/ins&gt;</pre>
  </section>
</body>

</html>